---
// Figure: Bounded verification is not surveillance
// Four actors: Holder, Checker, Public service, Oversight.
// Issuer as a light supporting node.
// Shows only what must flow, what the holder can inspect,
// and what must not become a cross-service behavioural record.
---

<div class="reveal my-12 md:my-16">
  <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border overflow-hidden" style="background: rgba(11,11,17,0.6);">
    <div class="p-6 md:p-8">

      <div class="mb-6">
        <p class="text-text-tertiary text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-1">Design boundary</p>
        <h3 class="text-text-primary font-display font-bold text-lg tracking-tight">Bounded verification is not surveillance</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="w-full overflow-x-auto">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 760 340" class="w-full min-w-[560px]" role="img" aria-label="Four-actor system diagram: holder, checker, public service, and oversight. Shows required flow, a holder inspection path, and a forbidden zone that cannot become a cross-service behavioural record.">
          <defs>
            <marker id="vvs-arrow" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="9" refY="5" markerWidth="7" markerHeight="7" orient="auto-start-reverse">
              <path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.6)"/>
            </marker>
            <marker id="vvs-arrow-holder" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="9" refY="5" markerWidth="7" markerHeight="7" orient="auto-start-reverse">
              <path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="rgba(244,114,182,0.7)"/>
            </marker>
          </defs>

          <!-- Issuer — light supporting node -->
          <g opacity="0.7">
            <rect x="40" y="30" width="150" height="42" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,0.05)" stroke="rgba(167,139,250,0.35)" stroke-dasharray="4 3" stroke-width="1"/>
            <text x="115" y="55" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.65)" font-family="'Syne', system-ui" font-size="11" font-weight="500">Issuer · supporting</text>
          </g>
          <line x1="115" y1="72" x2="115" y2="130" stroke="rgba(167,139,250,0.3)" stroke-dasharray="3 3" stroke-width="1"/>

          <!-- Core row: Holder → Checker → Public service -->
          <g>
            <rect x="40" y="140" width="150" height="56" rx="8" fill="rgba(244,114,182,0.08)" stroke="rgba(244,114,182,0.55)" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <text x="115" y="165" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.9)" font-family="'Syne', system-ui" font-size="13" font-weight="600">Holder</text>
            <text x="115" y="182" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.55)" font-family="'Inter', system-ui" font-size="10">the person</text>
          </g>

          <g>
            <rect x="305" y="140" width="150" height="56" rx="8" fill="rgba(245,158,11,0.08)" stroke="rgba(245,158,11,0.55)" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <text x="380" y="165" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.9)" font-family="'Syne', system-ui" font-size="13" font-weight="600">Checker</text>
            <text x="380" y="182" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.55)" font-family="'Inter', system-ui" font-size="10">verification service</text>
          </g>

          <g>
            <rect x="570" y="140" width="150" height="56" rx="8" fill="rgba(74,222,128,0.08)" stroke="rgba(74,222,128,0.55)" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <text x="645" y="165" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.9)" font-family="'Syne', system-ui" font-size="13" font-weight="600">Public service</text>
            <text x="645" y="182" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.55)" font-family="'Inter', system-ui" font-size="10">or relying party</text>
          </g>

          <!-- Forward flows -->
          <line x1="190" y1="168" x2="305" y2="168" stroke="rgba(232,232,240,0.55)" stroke-width="1.3" marker-end="url(#vvs-arrow)"/>
          <text x="247" y="158" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.75)" font-family="'JetBrains Mono', monospace" font-size="10">claims</text>

          <line x1="455" y1="168" x2="570" y2="168" stroke="rgba(232,232,240,0.55)" stroke-width="1.3" marker-end="url(#vvs-arrow)"/>
          <text x="512" y="158" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.75)" font-family="'JetBrains Mono', monospace" font-size="10">result</text>

          <!-- Holder inspection back channel -->
          <path d="M 305 195 Q 220 225 190 195" fill="none" stroke="rgba(244,114,182,0.7)" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-dasharray="4 3" marker-end="url(#vvs-arrow-holder)"/>
          <text x="247" y="235" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(244,114,182,0.85)" font-family="'JetBrains Mono', monospace" font-size="10">holder can inspect</text>

          <!-- Oversight node -->
          <g>
            <rect x="305" y="265" width="150" height="48" rx="8" fill="rgba(167,139,250,0.1)" stroke="rgba(167,139,250,0.6)" stroke-width="1.2"/>
            <text x="380" y="288" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.9)" font-family="'Syne', system-ui" font-size="13" font-weight="600">Oversight · redress</text>
            <text x="380" y="304" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(232,232,240,0.55)" font-family="'Inter', system-ui" font-size="10">complaints · appeal · audit</text>
          </g>

          <!-- Oversight connections (dashed, light) -->
          <line x1="380" y1="196" x2="380" y2="265" stroke="rgba(167,139,250,0.4)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3 3"/>
          <line x1="180" y1="196" x2="330" y2="265" stroke="rgba(167,139,250,0.25)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3 3"/>
          <line x1="605" y1="196" x2="435" y2="265" stroke="rgba(167,139,250,0.25)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3 3"/>

          <!-- Forbidden boundary -->
          <rect x="570" y="260" width="150" height="58" rx="8" fill="rgba(239,68,68,0.04)" stroke="rgba(239,68,68,0.35)" stroke-dasharray="4 3" stroke-width="1"/>
          <text x="645" y="282" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(239,68,68,0.8)" font-family="'Syne', system-ui" font-size="11" font-weight="600">Must not become</text>
          <text x="645" y="296" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(239,68,68,0.7)" font-family="'Inter', system-ui" font-size="10">a cross service</text>
          <text x="645" y="310" text-anchor="middle" fill="rgba(239,68,68,0.7)" font-family="'Inter', system-ui" font-size="10">behavioural record</text>
        </svg>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
  <p class="text-text-tertiary text-xs mt-3 text-center italic">
    Bounded verification is not surveillance. The difference is a design decision, not an emergent property.
  </p>
</div>
